'''Hayada Cuntada Aduunka''' ({{lang-en|''World Food Programme''}}; {{lang-ar|برنامج الأغذية العالمي}}) (loo soo gaabiyo: '''WFP''') waa waa waaxda 
[[Cunto|gargaarka cuntada]] ee hay'ada [[Qaramada Midoobay]] iyo ururka ugu wayn caalamka ee ka warbixiya [[gaajo|gaajada]] isla markaana dhiirigeliya amniga cuntada.<ref>{{cite web |last=WFP |title=Mission Statement |url=http://www.wfp.org/about/mission-statement |publisher=WFP |accessdate=2 November 2013}}</ref> 
Sida ay sheegtay hay'adani waxay gargaar cunto gaadhsiisaa sanad kasta dad dhan [[milyan|80 milyan]] oo ku kala nool 75 wadan.<ref>[https://www.wfp.org/about About WFP]. WFP.org. Retrieved 2015-04-08</ref> 
Magaca hayada marka la fasiro oo noqonaya Barnaamijka Cuntada Aduunka waxa xarunta ugu sareeysa ku leedahay magaalada [[Roma]] wadanka [[Talyaaniga]], iyo in ka badan ilaa 80 xafiis dacalada aduunka.
Intaas waxaa dheer, muhiimada koowaad hayadu waxay siisa dadka awoodi waayay ineey cunto u helaan naftooda iyo qoyskooda sababo la xidhiidha [[dagaal]]o, [[xanuun]]o, musiibo dabiici ah (sida [[daad]], duufaan, [[abaar]]o, [[dhulgariir]] iwm) darteed. 

Guud ahaanHay'ada Cuntada Aduunka oo loo soo gaabiyo ''WFP'' waxay xubin ka tahay  [[UN|Kooxda Horumarka Qaramada Midoobay]] iyo waaxda Golaha Go'aaminta.<ref>[http://www.undg.org/index.cfm?P=23 Executive Committee]. Undg.org. Retrieved on 2012-01-15.</ref>
